description:
Cuticle Scissors-Curved.

Finest quality stainless steel cuticle scissors with precision, thinner & shorter blades to safely & easily trim excess skin from the nail base where healthy nail growth begins. With a satin steel finish & black coated handles, these professional scissors are durable, functional & long-lasting.

Beauty Tips

-Overgrown cuticles should be trimmed to prevent further tearing of cuticle & avoid the development of painful hangnails.

-May be used on toenail cuticles.

-Apply Manicare Cuticle Oil after use to replenish moisture to the nail bed & cuticles.Â
